node.text:
@deepak_karra 😍 posts the most beautiful and rarest birds on the planet! Which is your favorite, from 1-10? 🌎
Follow @deepak_karra if you haven’t already

The featured birds are 
1. Pink Robin 
2. Rose Robin
3. Diamond Firetail
4. Spotted Pardalote
5. Rufous Fantail 
6. Superb Fairy-Wren 
7. Australian Ringneck 
8. Rainbow Lorikeet 
9. Scarlet Robin
10. Eastern Spinebill
